Class Account

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.djzass.medipoint.entity.Account
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    android.os.Parcelable

    public class Account
extends java.lang.Object
implements android.os.Parcelable
    Account class to represent a user account for our application. To enable object passing between activities, this class extends Parcelable.
